{"tid":1238675,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：修例風波重創香港國外聲譽　倡香港商會組團外訪","createTime":"2019-06-18T01:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T03:29:49.000Z","uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"842bd63e039be7c3fd1f22fc707a57b216fbafaf","tid":1238675,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:53:19.000Z","msg":"上任特首梁振英首度公開評論現任特首林鄭月娥修訂《逃犯條例》，他今早（17日）在fb貼文稱，事件「重創香港在國外的聲譽」，建議香港各大商會馬上組團連續出訪，幫助解釋。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英指出，他建議由香港各大商會連續出訪解釋，是因「對外的解釋說明工作，我們不能僅靠中國駐外的使領館，不能僅靠力量單薄的香港特區經貿辦事處，更不能靠外國傳媒」，「各商會在特區政府作出讓步後接受修改方案，對整件事的來龍去脈最為清楚，因此最有發言權」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190618/s00001/1560821231480/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E9%87%8D%E5%89%B5%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E8%81%B2%E8%AD%BD-%E5%80%A1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E7%B5%84%E5%9C%98%E5%A4%96%E8%A8%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190618%2Fs00001%2F1560821231480%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2589%25B5%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%2581%25B2%25E8%25AD%25BD-%25E5%2580%25A1%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%259C%2598%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25A8%25AA&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXn0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=dbd1db2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190618%2Fs00001%2F1560821231480%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%